    <item>
      <title>南非的DA警告贫困“荒地”没有GDP提升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/south-africa-s-da-warns-of-wasteland-of-poverty-without-gdp-growth-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非的民主联盟提出了改革以加强经济增长，并要求进行支出审查，因为它阻止了提高增值税的惊喜计划，从而推迟了年度预算的表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/south-africa-s-da-warns-of-wasteland-of-poverty-without-gdp-growth-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 07:56:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Macron和Starmer前往华盛顿，游说乌克兰帮助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/macron-and-starmer-head-to-washington-to-lobby-for-ukraine-help</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统伊曼纽尔·马克龙（Emmanuel Macron）和英国总理凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）将于本周与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统会面，因为他们试图在华盛顿和莫斯科之间正在进行的谈判中扮演欧洲角色，以结束俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/macron-and-starmer-head-to-washington-to-lobby-for-ukraine-help</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 07:52:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胜利后，德国保守派面临着狭窄的权力之路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/german-conservatives-face-narrow-path-to-power-after-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国保守派领导人弗里德里希·梅尔斯（Friedrich Merz）在周日的大选中成为赢家，但结果使他的一集中的一条清晰的权力途径紧迫，紧迫地行动以迅速成立政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/german-conservatives-face-narrow-path-to-power-after-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 06:49:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>边缘政党收获后，德国的债务制动器改革有疑问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/german-fringe-parties-strong-showing-clouds-path-to-debt-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国面临着更宽大的财政政策的有限途径，周日议会选举威胁要减少下一步政府的选择，试图将经济摆脱漫长的停滞之阵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/german-fringe-parties-strong-showing-clouds-path-to-debt-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 05:05:25 GMT</pubDate>
